---
title: Char Siu Beef & Veggie Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Sesame Seeds
description: Elevate your dining experience with this beef and veggie-packed stir-fry! Sticky and fragrant, this dish is ready in a blink of
an eye and will satisfy all your stir-fry needs. Fluffy jasmine rice is a must to soak up all that rich sticky sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65a8c47a39e22d4840d70fc8-46cb63b9.jpeg
